name: Milla Jovovich
description:
Milla Jovovich is an Ukrainian-born actress, known for her performance as Alice in Resident Evil. According to the internet, she is also a supermodel, fashion designer, singer and public figure, but I don't know about all that.

The embed has been trained with my usual settings on SD 1.5 and works well on most 1.5 based models.

If you enjoy my creations and want to support me or have a face you'd like to commission, consider supporting me on Ko-Fi or Buy Me A Coffee :)
